1
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:53,730
Long time no see

2
00:02:05,460 --> 00:02:06,680
Does Yezi know?

3
00:02:25,570 --> 00:02:27,190
This is what Yezi asked you to find

4
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:41,050
You are braver than me

5
00:02:43,810 --> 00:02:44,950
Xiang Zeyi

6
00:04:40,050 --> 00:04:47,160
[09. We are willing to wait, because we had promise]

7
00:05:35,650 --> 00:05:38,590
Are you insane? You trying to call everyone over in middle of the night?

8
00:05:39,110 --> 00:05:41,540
What are you doing here in middle of the night?

9
00:05:42,990 --> 00:05:49,790
You followed me -Put it in better words. I was on my way to the bathroom, and out of blue sneaking on you

10
00:05:50,090 --> 00:05:51,600
Right

11
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:59,090
Has our Casanova turned into Romeo now?

12
00:06:04,220 --> 00:06:05,440
Keep it a secret

13
00:06:06,700 --> 00:06:08,040
What do I get?

14
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:17,560
I will ask my girl to say good words about you -Deal

15
00:06:19,620 --> 00:06:21,220
Keep your words

16
00:06:22,650 --> 00:06:26,340
Show me your painting -I’m still painting -One sec.

17
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:30,970
Are you bragging about your girl? -Like you are a single man

18
00:06:33,110 --> 00:06:37,380
Kids, long time no see. Did anything new happen to you?

19
00:06:37,660 --> 00:06:43,380
I’ve received a call about how she is dating a man 20 years older than her

20
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:49,970
She was suffering a lot. Here Song Li wants to tell you, set yourself free

21
00:06:49,970 --> 00:06:56,710
Freedom is how you get happiness in life. I’m playing a song for you, called Blankness

22
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,090
What are you doing?

23
00:07:23,370 --> 00:07:24,670
Waiting for you

24
00:07:24,930 --> 00:07:26,470
I’m here. Come over

25
00:07:27,110 --> 00:07:30,810
I’m coming

26
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:36,590
Put your foot back. What if you fall down? -Boring

27
00:07:36,930 --> 00:07:40,650
You are the unfunny one, the unromantic one

28
00:07:40,990 --> 00:07:49,980
Why are you laughing since I’m not funny? -I'm sneering -Sneering

29
00:07:49,980 --> 00:07:51,350
Fine

30
00:07:52,620 --> 00:07:54,330
Keep sneering

31
00:07:55,340 --> 00:08:03,650
What are you going to do? Stop running that fast. -Sneering -Cut it out

32
00:08:03,650 --> 00:08:04,850
What’s this?

33
00:08:08,130 --> 00:08:09,310
What?

34
00:08:15,530 --> 00:08:17,020
For me?

35
00:08:43,780 --> 00:08:49,830
I didn’t know you’d do things like this -There are many things you don’t know about

36
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:54,140
But I allow you to take your time to know me

37
00:08:55,820 --> 00:09:05,000
Isn’t this romantic for you? -Yes, you are funny -What do you mean by that?

38
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:19,640
No one is taking it from you, you can just put it here

39
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:23,680
This is your first present to me, it means a lot

40
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:30,580
Well, do you like it?

41
00:09:33,900 --> 00:09:35,050
Not bad

42
00:09:36,110 --> 00:09:41,410
Give it back if you don’t like it -It’s mine, don’t break it -Give it back since you don’t like it

43
00:09:41,770 --> 00:09:43,370
So you like it

44
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:48,020
Do I get any rewards?

45
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:08,120
In fact

46
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:13,760
I like drawing since I was a kid

47
00:10:18,100 --> 00:10:24,010
Stop looking at me with your admired eyes -I won’t look at you then -Look at me

48
00:10:28,390 --> 00:10:39,470
I’ve always had the dream that one day I can also create arts of my own style and known by the world

49
00:10:39,470 --> 00:10:43,510
Keep pursuing your dream, don’t give up on who you are

50
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:56,960
Thank you -You are welcome

51
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:05,210
Thank you -You are heavy

52
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:21,480
You looked happy before. Why are you being upset?

53
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:27,920
Xiang Zeyi, you be the judge of this -Did you fight? -How do you know?

54
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:35,200
Who can control your emotions but Liu Xinran?

55
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:37,180
That’s not fair

56
00:11:38,580 --> 00:11:42,770
But this time you have to be on my side -Say it

57
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:51,030
What is love?

58
00:11:55,890 --> 00:12:00,920
I don’t get it. Aren’t two people being together to have fun?

59
00:12:01,230 --> 00:12:07,180
In our age, not being in crazy love means wasting of time

60
00:12:08,260 --> 00:12:11,550
But women, I don’t get them

61
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:18,770
They can only think about work and future, about that freaking unreal result

62
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:26,160
Not everything in this world has to have a result. Why do people live if they know results of all things?

63
00:12:28,770 --> 00:12:33,150
Have you thought about that she is just afraid of losing you?

64
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:37,290
Nothing every problem can be solved by I love you

65
00:12:38,660 --> 00:12:44,800
What does a woman what from a man? A promise

66
00:12:47,870 --> 00:12:49,280
What about your promise to Yezi?

67
00:12:53,380 --> 00:12:54,690
Soon

68
00:13:16,510 --> 00:13:18,390
Hello, here is the Xiang Zeyi you ordered

69
00:13:22,460 --> 00:13:24,970
I didn’t mean to be late

70
00:13:26,590 --> 00:13:34,370
Don’t be mean to me. I had a thing in school. Don’t be upset

71
00:13:34,370 --> 00:13:42,110
What’s wrong? -She is mad -What do you want to drink? -As always -OK

72
00:13:42,110 --> 00:13:45,660
Make it taste bad for him -Mean girl

73
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:57,140
What? -None of your business -It is my business

74
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:01,880
What’s this?

75
00:14:05,050 --> 00:14:06,680
I don’t want to look anyway

76
00:14:25,510 --> 00:14:27,130
Not looking

77
00:14:56,020 --> 00:14:58,440
I can draw one for you everyday if you like

78
00:14:59,860 --> 00:15:03,410
Then I will have a full box when I graduate

79
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:11,010
That box will be my proposing gift

80
00:15:13,290 --> 00:15:14,790
Who is marrying you

81
00:15:16,330 --> 00:15:24,790
I wonder what my bride looks like -Ma’am listen to him -You brought it up

82
00:15:27,710 --> 00:15:29,930
Here -Thank you

83
00:15:34,450 --> 00:15:36,690
OK mean girl

84
00:15:39,410 --> 00:15:43,280
You

85
00:15:44,740 --> 00:15:46,650
Mean girl, I’ll show you a trick

86
00:15:53,410 --> 00:15:54,520
You got lucky

87
00:15:59,010 --> 00:16:00,180
One more

88
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:18,090
You

89
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:12,690
Xiang Zeyi, long time no see -Right -Sit

90
00:17:13,940 --> 00:17:17,040
What do you want to drink today? -Whatever

91
00:17:20,450 --> 00:17:24,000
Where is your girlfriend? -We broke up

92
00:17:29,130 --> 00:17:30,500
I’m sorry

93
00:17:31,630 --> 00:17:41,360
How are you? -As always, running this bar

94
00:18:59,120 --> 00:19:00,430
Just try

95
00:19:03,730 --> 00:19:05,390
Here

96
00:19:07,370 --> 00:19:08,960
How is it?

97
00:19:11,810 --> 00:19:15,560
Sweet -Of course it is -I meant you

98
00:19:17,780 --> 00:19:21,550
How many girls did you tell this to? -You don’t want to know

99
00:19:40,580 --> 00:19:41,810
What are you doing?

100
00:19:45,160 --> 00:19:52,250
Yezi (means leaf in Chinese), is wings that can’t fly

101
00:19:53,070 --> 00:19:59,670
Wings are leaves in sky

102
00:20:01,010 --> 00:20:08,650
Heaven shouldn’t be just in dreams

103
00:20:08,950 --> 00:20:12,500
It’s just that I’ve forgotten

104
00:20:12,820 --> 00:20:17,900
How I started to fly

105
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:32,390
Being alone is also a party of one

106
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:42,070
Love starts with simply being together

107
00:20:42,340 --> 00:20:45,680
But I begin to forget

108
00:20:46,010 --> 00:20:50,310
How someone was keeping my accompany

109
00:20:50,610 --> 00:20:58,260
On my own I eat and travel, walk and stop

110
00:20:58,550 --> 00:21:06,560
On my own I read and write, talk to my own mind

111
00:21:06,810 --> 00:21:15,510
But where does my mind go, I can’t say

112
00:21:15,870 --> 00:21:23,840
I think I’m feeling more than just liking you

113
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:39,590
Why are you avoiding me? -I told you there won’t be result between us

114
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:46,470
Liu Xinran, what do you mean by result? Do we know about tomorrow when we are living today?

115
00:21:46,710 --> 00:21:49,600
Tell me, do you know why will you die? -You

116
00:21:49,890 --> 00:21:51,010
Whatever you say

117
00:21:51,570 --> 00:21:53,450
Let go

118
00:21:53,730 --> 00:21:56,820
One more question and I’m leaving -Fine

119
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:59,440
Do you still like me? -No

120
00:22:01,100 --> 00:22:02,530
OK I’m leaving

121
00:22:05,130 --> 00:22:06,200
Daniao

122
00:22:07,060 --> 00:22:08,520
Zhang Daniao

123
00:22:08,910 --> 00:22:10,480
I’m here

124
00:22:12,760 --> 00:22:15,530
Don’t be upset. I apologize

125
00:22:16,440 --> 00:22:21,700
I can’t give you the result you want yet, but I also can’t leave you

126
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:26,710
I can only promise you that I won’t let you get hurt as long as I’m with you

127
00:22:29,970 --> 00:22:31,010
Here

128
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:40,610
I made this ring on my own. It looks a bit ugly but I still hope you’d like it

129
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:49,930
You can’t lie to me anymore -I won’t

130
00:22:53,250 --> 00:22:54,410
Come

131
00:23:16,500 --> 00:23:17,480
Hey

132
00:23:18,730 --> 00:23:19,930
I want

133
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:22,590
I want to ask if you are available tomorrow

134
00:23:26,020 --> 00:23:30,380
My friend gave me two movie tickets so I wonder if you have time tomorrow

135
00:23:32,870 --> 00:23:34,380
I’m not interested

136
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:47,220
President, stop wasting time on me. Go ask someone else

137
00:24:00,910 --> 00:24:03,010
I know, I’m all ready

138
00:24:07,370 --> 00:24:08,780
See you tomorrow

139
00:24:10,670 --> 00:24:12,450
Good night

140
00:24:14,300 --> 00:24:17,470
So nice having someone to say good night every day

141
00:24:19,970 --> 00:24:22,100
When will my Yuan Lang be brighter?

142
00:24:24,100 --> 00:24:30,260
Zhuzi, do you think I’ll get used to it if someday he stops saying good night to me?

143
00:24:30,620 --> 00:24:34,950
Your Xiang Zeyi is romantic enough to say good night to you when he is 180 years old

144
00:24:36,370 --> 00:24:38,980
You are thinking too much.

145
00:24:39,690 --> 00:24:45,640
Life is short. Just enjoy as much as you can when you are still alive

146
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:49,700
You have a point -Just listen to me

147
00:24:49,920 --> 00:24:53,780
I will remember what love expert Zhuxuan said to me

148
00:25:11,070 --> 00:25:15,480
Keep your eyes closed -Are we there yet? -Almost

149
00:25:18,390 --> 00:25:19,830
OK

150
00:25:31,780 --> 00:25:33,650
Do you like this?

151
00:25:36,530 --> 00:25:43,390
Do you like it or not? -Did you prepare this? -Yes

152
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:48,620
Why do you hang it here?

153
00:25:59,310 --> 00:26:07,210
It’s not simply a painting. It’s more like a promise to me

154
00:26:08,730 --> 00:26:11,310
As long as it hangs here, I’ll always

155
00:26:18,050 --> 00:26:19,900
I’ll always be here for you

156
00:26:30,340 --> 00:26:36,930
Last time, I’ll quit if you still can’t catch -OK ready

157
00:26:39,170 --> 00:26:41,380
Are you OK? -I quit -It’s the racquet

158
00:26:41,380 --> 00:26:43,170
One more round -No, you just can’t catch

159
00:26:43,170 --> 00:26:48,240
One more -Let’s take a break

160
00:26:49,720 --> 00:26:51,370
Are you alright?

161
00:26:53,010 --> 00:26:54,520
Are you having a fever?

162
00:26:54,990 --> 00:26:58,340
I’m fine -Have some medicine and watch how it goes before going to the medicals

163
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:08,500
Daniao told me that Xiang Zeyi caught cold -Didn’t he?

164
00:27:09,630 --> 00:27:14,290
Yezi, what naughty thing did you do with Xiang Zeyi?

165
00:27:14,290 --> 00:27:20,180
Stop kidding with a patient -What did I say? Eve and Adam are meant to be together

166
00:27:20,690 --> 00:27:28,050
That’s what you meant -Or what did you think? -You are so not the pure girl I know -Whatever

167
00:27:30,130 --> 00:27:33,830
I need water. This is hers -Xinze

168
00:27:34,720 --> 00:27:39,570
DId Daniao mention about Xiang Zeyi’s condition? -Daniao

169
00:27:39,570 --> 00:27:42,930
Even Xiang Zeyi is sick, he is stronger than you

170
00:27:42,930 --> 00:27:47,270
He is a man. If he is weaker than you, just break up with him

171
00:27:48,670 --> 00:27:57,380
Do you want to play more? -Sure, let me have some water -I’m coming too -Come on

172
00:29:13,530 --> 00:29:14,700
Mr.Shao

173
00:29:15,810 --> 00:29:22,730
What are you doing here? -Am I not welcomed? -Of course you are. Come in please

174
00:29:33,540 --> 00:29:35,940
Sit down, what do you want to drink -Anything would be fine

175
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:51,160
No need to clean up. It feels more like working

176
00:29:51,840 --> 00:29:56,610
A good place to stand back on your feet -Stop teasing me

177
00:29:58,120 --> 00:30:02,140
I invited you to my company after you graduated

178
00:30:03,080 --> 00:30:07,030
That invitation is still valid

179
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:20,020
I can’t even draw well an oil painting now

180
00:30:21,660 --> 00:30:26,750
You do need time to pick if up since you haven’t touched it for years

181
00:30:30,580 --> 00:30:32,250
What if I can never pick it up?

182
00:30:34,680 --> 00:30:39,700
That’s not the person I know. You were brave and passionate

183
00:30:39,700 --> 00:30:46,400
You had your personal style and you were special enough to say love to a girl in front of that many people

184
00:30:51,820 --> 00:30:56,310
Maybe time can change many things

185
00:30:57,210 --> 00:31:04,540
But since you’ve decided to start over, don’t ever give up nor hold onto this negative emotion

186
00:31:05,680 --> 00:31:12,070
Remember that chances are always for people that are persistent and prepared

187
00:31:17,980 --> 00:31:21,980
I handed you my business card when you won the award

188
00:31:23,730 --> 00:31:34,370
After all these years I still hold my position, it depends on you now

189
00:31:36,160 --> 00:31:45,720
You are still the same person. Go to the old places, meet your muses, find your heart

190
00:32:40,020 --> 00:32:41,810
Lin Sen come sit

191
00:32:45,810 --> 00:32:48,140
What? -What happened?

192
00:32:48,140 --> 00:32:55,750
What do you mean? -Stop playing fool with me, I mean between you and Yezi

193
00:33:07,370 --> 00:33:12,710
Lin Sen, is Xiang Zeyi back?

194
00:33:16,460 --> 00:33:18,150
He is back, isn’t he?

195
00:33:29,420 --> 00:33:35,420
I was wondering why Yezi suddenly brought up about that sticker that day when you were proposing

196
00:33:38,610 --> 00:33:43,270
Lin Sen, what’s your plan now? -I don’t care if he is back or not

197
00:33:46,650 --> 00:33:48,950
I don’t want Yezi to get hurt anymore

198
00:34:03,950 --> 00:34:05,460
Are you feeling unwell?

199
00:34:10,080 --> 00:34:16,950
I’m fine. I’m just worried about you and Yezi that my stomach hurts

200
00:34:18,940 --> 00:34:21,210
Come to me and take a check if you feel unwell

201
00:34:21,510 --> 00:34:24,430
Or Yuan Lang will worry to death if there is really something

202
00:34:24,730 --> 00:34:30,740
Do you still have time thinking about us? Just worry about yourself and Yezi. I’m fine

203
00:34:32,710 --> 00:34:34,710
I have things to do. Call me

204
00:35:44,070 --> 00:35:45,540
I thought I love you the most

205
00:35:49,310 --> 00:35:51,480
But I made you scared for so long

206
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:05,150
I'm sorry
